{
  "stem": "868.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ready?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was fortunate to find this couple, man and wife, who operated a portrait studio in Montpelier called Studio Harry, H-A-R-R-Y.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was hidden there in the darkroom in the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You must realize that this already was a great risk to the people hiding me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But living there, I started to pick up basic elements of photography.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I spent my time, ironically, in the darkroom in the back developing pictures of German soldiers, who had come in to have their portraits taken to send to their wives, or sweethearts, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I stayed there for quite a while [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] until a new law came out saying everybody needs new identification papers, new French identification papers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they thought that this would be a good opportunity for, for me to acquire one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a-- I had a false one on the name of Paul Boreel, B-O-R-E-E-L, born in some French town and so forth.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was a fake one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The new law said you have to turn in the fake one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you have to turn in the previous one and get a new one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we travelled to a town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The husband came with me because he needed one, one, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was born in England.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that didn't go over very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he figured he, too, was going to ask for a new one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were out of there, feeling suddenly like having been granted permission to, to live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were now French with the new cards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing could stop us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Italian authorities had designated various areas as residence forcee, which means you had to live in that area.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
